                  {
                    "ref": "lab-mo-egfr-0609",
                    "label": "eGFR 6/9/2026"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "text": "Warfarin for mechanical mitral valve — do not hold/reverse without cardiology; new antibiotics will potentiate INR, recheck in 3–5 days per anticoagulation clinic instructions",
                "severity": "caution",
                "sources": [
                  {
                    "ref": "bin-mo-pdf-acc-fax",
                    "label": "Anticoagulation flowsheet 7/10/2026"
                  },
